nd your place in the world. <br><br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Friends and foes brought to life in expressive hand-drawn 2D animation!<br></li><li>Talk to lots of cute and strange characters as you explore the land of Salia!<br></li><li>Explore five unique areas filled with their own special enemies, villages, and bosses! <br></li><li>Upgrade your blade at the blacksmith's shop for stronger attacks!<br></li><li>Follow a heartfelt story that deals with themes of identity and self love!<br></li><li>Try to make the world just a little bit better! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281860/extras/741498e8aee18ea82f1ac933ec96ab54.poster.avif?t=1734722122\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281860/extras/741498e8aee18ea82f1ac933ec96ab54.webm?t=1734722122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281860/extras/741498e8aee18ea82f1ac933ec96ab54.mp4?t=1734722122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281860/extras/ebbbfa0876b2cfd1c9a9569ecb661cb8.poster.avif?t=1734722122\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281860/extras/ebbbfa0876b2cfd1c9a9569ecb661cb8.webm?t=1734722122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281860/extras/ebbbfa0876b2cfd1c9a9569ecb661cb8.mp4?t=1734722122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
